strings: <voice_0x01001399><se_high>Red: So movin' the 'andle makes the water go down, eh?

<voice_0x0100139A><se_high>Red: Thanks for that!
Now I can get even further ahead of ya!
<voice_0x0100139B><se_high>Red: Bad luck, eh! Must be a bit annoyin' that you figured it out but I'm the one to benefit!
